  "title": "Accountant #79349",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Construction</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Accountant</strong></li><li>Working Location: Expo</li><li>Working Hours: 5 days (Mon – Fri, 9.00am – 6.45pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic salary up to $5,000 + AWS + Variable Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent Role</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Maintain a full set of accounts, including accounts receivable, accounts payable, and the general ledger.</li><li>Handle tax matters, including quarterly GST filings and corporate income tax.</li><li>Prepare monthly, quarterly, and annual financial statements.</li><li>Reconcile bank accounts and other balance sheet accounts.</li><li>Support internal and external audits.</li><li>Work with the finance team and other departments to keep financial data accurate and current.</li><li>Identify process improvement opportunities and implement more efficient financial practices.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Degree or professional qualification in Accounting or a related field.</li><li>At least 3 years of experience in a full-cycle accounting role; experience in the construction industry is an advantage.</li><li>Solid understanding of financial accounting principles, including GST regulations and reporting requirements.</li><li>Proficient with ABSS (MYOB) and QuickBooks accounting software.</li><li>Good knowledge of accounting principles, tax regulations, and financial best practices.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#79349 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
